# Oshlink Website — Clone of AutoSynTech.com

Build a premium AI Automation Agency website for **Oshlink**, closely mirroring the structure and design of autosyntech.com but rebranded with Oshlink's identity.

## Brand Identity

| Element | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Company Name | **Oshlink** |
| Primary Dark | `#1C2321` |
| Accent Color | `#984447` |
| Tagline | *Building the automated workforce of tomorrow.* |
| Contact Email | `info@oshlink.com` |

