## Proposed Changes

### Project Setup

#### [NEW] Vite project scaffold

Initialize a Vite vanilla JS project in `c:\Users\llsadmin\OneDrive\Desktop\oshlink\` with the following structure:

```
oshlink/
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── main.js
├── sections/
│   ├── hero.js
│   ├── stats.js
│   ├── calculator.js
│   ├── services.js
│   ├── audit.js
│   └── footer.js
├── components/
│   ├── navbar.js
│   └── logo-ticker.js
└── public/
    └── assets/
```

---

### Sections to Build (in order)

#### 1. Hero Section
- Large headline: **"YOUR TEAM WAS HIRED TO THINK."** + sub: **"Let AI Do The Rest."**
- Body paragraph about custom AI infrastructures
- Pill tags: AI Automation, Intelligent Workflows, Voice Agents
- Two CTAs: "Start Your AI Audit" (primary) + "Talk to Our Voice Agent" (secondary)
- Animated SVG background paths
- Fade-in text animations

#### 2. Trusted By Logo Ticker
- Infinitely scrolling horizontal logo strip
- Placeholder company logos (generated or SVG placeholders)

#### 3. Stats Section
- Three large animated counters: 500+, $2M+, 99.6%
- Descriptive labels beneath each

#### 4. ROI Calculator
- Headline: "The Real Cost of Manual Work"
- Three interactive range sliders (Employees, Hours/Week, Hourly Wage)
- Real-time savings calculation display
- Results card with Year 1 Savings, Cost Reduction %, Annual Cost, Timeline

#### 5. Services Section ("What We Build For You")
- 6 service cards in a staggered/hexagonal grid layout
- Cards flip on hover to reveal detailed descriptions
- Services: Client Acquisition, Voice Infrastructure, Workflow Automation, CRM Management, Customer Support, Document Processing

#### 6. Efficiency Audit Form
- Multi-field form: Company Name, Revenue, Team Size, Growth, Industry
- Styled dark card with accent-colored inputs and CTA
- "START AUDIT" button

#### 7. Footer
- Newsletter signup with email input
- Three-column link grid (Services, Resources, Contact)
- Social media icons (LinkedIn, Twitter, Facebook, Instagram)
- Copyright line

#### 8. Floating Bottom Navbar
- Glassmorphism pill bar fixed at bottom
- Links: Home icon, Services, Start Audit (CTA)

---

### Design System (`style.css`)

- **Colors**: `#1C2321` (dark bg), `#984447` (accent replacing gold), white text
- **Typography**: Google Font "Inter" or "Outfit" for modern feel
- **Effects**: Glassmorphism nav, card hover flips, smooth scrolling, gradient overlays
- **Animations**: CSS keyframes for fade-ins, counter animations in JS, infinite ticker scroll

---

## Verification Plan

### Browser Visual Review
1. Run `npm run dev` in `c:\Users\llsadmin\OneDrive\Desktop\oshlink\`
2. Open the local dev URL in the browser
3. Scroll through all sections and verify:
   - Hero text and CTAs render correctly
   - Logo ticker scrolls infinitely
   - Stats counters animate on scroll
   - ROI Calculator sliders update values in real-time
   - Service cards flip on hover
   - Audit form fields and button are styled correctly
   - Footer layout is complete
   - Floating navbar is visible and functional
4. Resize browser to test responsive behavior at mobile/tablet breakpoints

> [!NOTE]
> This is a front-end only website build. No backend or API integrations are needed at this stage. The audit form will be a visual placeholder.
